Package: acediaR
Type: Package
Title: GPU-Accelerated Computing for R using CUDA
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Author: Aleksei M
Maintainer: Aleksei M <email@example.com>
Description: Provides CUDA-accelerated linear algebra operations and statistical functions for R, 
    enabling high-performance computing on NVIDIA GPUs. This package implements GPU kernels for 
    common mathematical operations including vector arithmetic, matrix operations, and statistical 
    computations.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
SystemRequirements: CUDA toolkit (>= 11.0), NVIDIA GPU with compute capability >= 5.0
